      <h1>I'm Brian Hafner. I help service businesses get found in AI answers.</h1>
      <p class="lead" style="max-width:760px;">I'm Brian Hafner, an AI Visibility consultant helping service businesses get cited, recommended, and quoted by ChatGPT, Gemini, and Google AI Overviews. Based in San Diego, I combine two decades of data and analytics experience with hands-on technical implementation — schema, entity clarity, and revenue attribution that proves the work is paying off.</p>
